<paragraphs xml:id="introduction">
<title>Introduction</title>

<p> The  is perhaps the most important descriptive and
computational tool in applied mathematics and the physical and life
sciences.
</p>


<paragraphs xml:id="change">
<title>Change</title>

<p>	Change, key to science (and calculus), is conveyed
by the . When we talk about change it is helpful to note,
</p>

<p><ul>
<li><p><m>\Delta</m> is mathematical shorthand for change
